	<h1 class="title">雷军也要做电影了，小米能打好电影这张牌吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">彭卡茜 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-05 09:58:50 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/20237/medium/20237.jpg?1451917428" alt="" />			
	</div>
