<div class="com-share" data-id="20237" data-title="《雷军也要做电影了，小米能打好电影这张牌吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/20237/medium/20237.jpg?1451917428" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/20237.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
